title: Themes Nest in Other Library
description: Themes are nesting within another library. Details: Themes are nesting within another library.
OB: Themes from one library are appearing within a different library.
EB: Themes should be contained only within their respective libraries and should not mix with themes from other libraries.
SR:
Steps to reproduce: 
1. Open the application. 
2. Navigate to the 'Themes' section. 
3. Observe that themes from one library are displayed within another library.
